      <title>Robinhood 计划回购高达 10 亿美元的股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/robinhood-jumps-on-plan-to-buy-back-up-to-1-billion-of-shares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[零售经纪公司 Robinhood Markets Inc. 宣布计划回购高达 10 亿美元的自有股票，随后其股价大幅上涨。]]></description>
